<!id: try-with-resources>
<!description: Suggest try-with-resources for AutoCloseable resources>
<!severity: warning>
<!minJavaVersion: 8>
<!tags: resources, safety>

// Hint-only: .close() on an AutoCloseable local variable not already in try-with-resources
"Consider using try-with-resources for AutoCloseable resource":
$x.close() :: isAutoCloseable($x) && !isInTryWithResourceBlock($x) && isLocalVariable($x)
;;
